title: 'Chain lock stuck'
body: 'Chain lock gets stuck and code changes automatically for some reason'

title: 'Quality issues'
body: 'The outer part is okay but the overall quality is not good. Stitching is very bad of inside cloth. The suitcase handle is not smooth to operate.'

title: 'Product defects'
body: 'I went with the luggage trolley bag and used it comfortably but on the way back the chain of the luggage ripped up. I purchased the trolley bag on 18th June 2023. Can you please help me repairing this as this is within the warranty period.'

title: 'How to register warranty'
body: 'In spite of scanning the QR code not able to register the warranty. Help in this issue how to register it'

title: 'Not nice quality'
body: Did not like it much. The zip gets stuck. Don't know how long will it last me
